projects.name: Road Lane Line Detection
projects.description: Developed a system for detecting road lane lines in real-time using machine learning techniques. Collected and pre-processed image datasets for training and testing the model. Implemented image processing techniques such as edge detection, color filtering, and perspective transformation. Developed and trained convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for lane detection. Evaluated model performance using metrics like accuracy, precision, and recall. Integrated the lane detection model with a real-time video feed to detect lane lines. Collaborated with team members to optimize the model and improve detection accuracy.

projects.name: Fast Food Website
projects.description: Designed and implemented the front-end interface using HTML, CSS, and React. Developed back-end services and RESTful APIs using Node.js and Express. Integrated MongoDB for storing user data, orders, and menu items. Implemented user authentication and authorization using JWT. Created a responsive design to ensure compatibility across various devices. Conducted usability testing to improve user experience and interface design.
